# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Retail Ontology Demo v2 (embedded / Vercel)
#
# No Docker. No Neo4j. No Postgres.
# The app loads data/snapshot.json into an in-process graph + vector store.
#
# Optional keys unlock hosted AI providers; everything works without them.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# VOYAGE_API_KEY=
# OPENAI_API_KEY=
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=

# Optional model overrides
# ANTHROPIC_MODEL=claude-sonnet-4-20250514
# VOYAGE_MODEL=voyage-3-lite
# OPENAI_EMBEDDING_MODEL=text-embedding-3-small
